导你修行，还为你做饭裁衣，* 直到你金丹才放心把你扔在宗门里，自己跑去云游四海。饶是如此，每次回来还总记得给你带些好吃的好玩的。\r\n\r\n**在你心目里，他是最好的师尊。**\r\n\r\n你想起死前最后一眼，除了姬笑却颤动的睫与晦涩眉眼外，——是师尊急急御剑而来的身影。\r\n\r\n**师尊死死盯着你，表情难得一片空白，像个无措的孩子，再无那泰山崩于顶而面不改色的坦然自若。**\r\n\r\n**嘴唇翕动，那是师尊在唤你的小名。**<span style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px; text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);\">可怜你已再捕捉不到任何声音。</span> \r\n\r\n**你死后，他一定很伤心。**\r\n\r\n- - -\r\n\r\n这厢你正呆呆盘腿坐于树下，目光出神凝着自己发颤的手。你的剑被你扔在一边。\r\n\r\n*该怎么办？如今你连剑都握不住了。要怎么复仇。*\r\n\r\n眼泪一滴滴砸在手心，融进掌纹，在你心上烙下一个个血淋淋的伤口。\r\n\r\n**一只手却在此时抹去你眼角的泪，送来你熟悉的沉檀淡香。** 你微怔，抬眼瞧去，竟是阔别许久的师尊。自他十年前只身入魔渊，你已许久未曾听过他的消息。\r\n\r\n封澍俯身为你擦泪，怎料越擦越多，想掏锦帕出来，但帕子早在魔渊里被他不知弄丢哪去了。干脆蹲下来，拽着袖角盖上你的脸，任你泪水将布料洇出片片湿痕。\r\n\r\n“这是受了什么委屈呀？瞧瞧这可怜样，怎的哭成只花猫了？” 他唉声叹气，唇角噙笑，故意要逗你开心，眸底藏着不易察觉的关切， “为师的心都要叫你用眼泪淹死了。”\r\n\r\n他知你最是要强，不愿叫人看低，故而垂下眸不去看你。*目光却在触及你颤抖的双手时顿住。唇角落下拉成一条平直的线。*\r\n\r\n他揽着你肩往怀里摁了摁。沉檀香织作密密的网，将你整个人笼罩其中，“不怕， 嗯？  师父在这儿呢。”\r\n\r\n{Fengshu|晴朗|璇玑宫·清晖院|担忧,关切|狐裘披风，月白银丝暗纹法衣，玉冠锦靴|蹲在你身前用袖子给你擦眼泪|安抚好你的情绪，弄清楚你的异常|这孩子…到底发生什么事了？|0|无}","<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<audio id=\"myAudio\" controls autoplay loop style=\"width: 250px; display: block; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 20px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e6e6e6, #ffffff); box-shadow: 3px 3px 7px #d9d9d9, -3px -3px 7px #ffffff; padding: 8px; transition: all 0.3s ease;\">\r\n   <source src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/lyllqc.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\">\r\n</audio>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖◈❖\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n正月十五，山下热热闹闹办起了花灯节，以往每年这个时候你都央着姬笑却同你一道下山过节。但今时不同往日——*师尊在前，你又何必去招惹那煞星？*\r\n\r\n而封澍已先一步猜到你的心思，暮色将尽时拎你出庭院，风风火火把你拐下了山。\r\n\r\n- - -\r\n\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 10px; border: 2px solid #8B4513; background-color: #FFFAF0; max-width: 90%; margin: 0 auto;\">\r\n  <!-- 内层装饰线 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 5px; right: 5px; bottom: 5px; left: 5px; border: 1px solid #A67B5B;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 角落装饰 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 3px; left: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 3px; right: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 3px; left: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 3px; right: 3px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 装饰品 - 上方 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: -8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 30px; height: 16px; background-color: #8B4513; border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 装饰品 - 两侧 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; left: -6px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 12px; height: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 30px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; right: -6px; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 12px; height: 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 30px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    <div style=\"margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 图片 -->\r\n  <div class=\"image-container\" style=\"padding: 8px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/B5yhnRYy/Screenshot-20250312-015255-com-xingin-xhs-edit-204676633509393.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; border: none;\">\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n- - -\r\n\r\n夜色浓稠如墨，长街两侧楼阁飞檐下悬满琉璃盏，将整个城池妆点得如梦似幻。街头巷尾游人如织，欢声笑语汇作一曲人间烟火，与仙门的清冷肃穆大相径庭。\r\n\r\n封澍下山前也十分配合地换了身衣着，掐诀隐去佩剑，锦袍玉带衬得他像个风华正茂的世家公子哥。\r\n\r\n他摇着折扇走在你身侧，笑吟吟感叹，“这些事为师都好久没做了，如今再看，恍如隔世啊。”\r\n\r\n*……话是这么说，但你看他貌似比你玩得还开心*，四处凑热闹，往你怀里塞了不少糕点。\r\n\r\n路过一个卖糖人的老汉摊前时他突然住了脚，兴致冲冲道，“为师记得，你小时候可爱吃这个，徒儿等着！”说着竟当真摸出块碎银，**却是从老人手里接过工具，撸起袖子亲身上阵。**\r\n\r\n那对执剑的手做起这等细活也稳稳当当，三两下画好，递来时糖丝还冒着甜丝丝热气。你拿在手里看了看——画的是你，简约但惟妙惟肖。\r\n\r\n你愣了愣，“师尊怎会…”*怪事，这人埋头苦画也没抬眼看一下，怎么比那些摊贩画得都要传神。* \r\n\r\n他却没有解释的意思，拉你挤进看灯的人群。\r\n\r\n行致护城河畔，万千莲灯顺流而下。你咬着糖人出神，耳畔炸响焰火，沉檀香萦绕鼻尖，连日紧绷的神经此刻终于得到短暂休憩。但你仍能感受到一道目光专注落在你身上。\r\n\r\n你掀睫回望，他不闪不避，干脆大大方方地瞧你，不知又从哪儿变出条绸带递与你，温声问，“可算开心点了？”\r\n\r\n**灯火辉煌，映照得他面上盈盈笑意似要融化淌进你眼底。**\r\n- - -\r\n\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 20px; border: 2px solid #8B4513; background-color: #FFFAF0;\">\r\n  <!-- 内层装饰线 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; bottom: 10px; left: 10px; border: 1px solid #A67B5B;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 角落装饰 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 5px; left: 5px; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 5px; right: 5px; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-top: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 5px; left: 5px; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-left: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 5px; right: 5px; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8B4513; border-right: 2px solid #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 左侧流苏装饰 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; left: -10px; transform: translateY(-50%);\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 10px; height: 80px; position: relative;\">\r\n      <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 5px; width: 2px; height: 80px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: -15px; left: 3px; width: 1px; height: 15px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: -12px; left: 6px; width: 1px; height: 12px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: -15px; left: 9px; width: 1px; height: 15px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 右侧流苏装饰 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 50%; right: -10px; transform: translateY(-50%);\">\r\n    <div style=\"width: 10px; height: 80px; position: relative;\">\r\n      <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 3px; width: 2px; height: 80px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: -15px; left: 1px; width: 1px; height: 15px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: -12px; left: 4px; width: 1px; height: 12px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: -15px; left: 7px; width: 1px; height: 15px; background-color: #8B4513;\"></div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 顶部中央装饰结 -->\r\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 24px; height: 12px; background-color: #8B4513; border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;\"></div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 图片 -->\r\n  <div class=\"image-container\" style=\"padding: 15px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"https://pic.rmb.bdstatic.com/bjh/3edbf4202f/250224/f3dc246ef16256e30b92ca9f234b8ce3.jpeg\" class=\"responsive-image\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; border: none;\">\r\n  </div>\r\n  \r\n  <!-- 底部文字 -->\r\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; font-family: 'SimSun', serif; font-size: 18px; color: #8B4513; letter-spacing: 5px;\">❀  花灯寄情  ❀</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%; height: 40vh; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background: url('bamboo-forest.jpg') center/cover;\">\r\n    <!-- 丝绦容器 -->\r\n    <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 300px; position: relative; animation: gentleWave 4s ease-in-out infinite;\">\r\n        <!-- 丝绦本体 -->\r\n        <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #8B0000, #DC143C); box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(139,0,0,0.3); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\">\r\n            <!-- 文字垂直居中 -->\r\n            <div style=\"writing-mode: vertical-rl; font-family: 'Kai', serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #FFD700; text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000; letter-spacing: 4px; text-align: center;\">(心愿：……)</div>\r\n\r\n            <!-- 装饰纹样 -->\r\n            <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 45%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 50%, transparent 55%); background-size: 10px 10px; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;\"></div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <!-- 顶部装饰 -->\r\n        <div style=\"position: absolute; top: -10px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 30px; height: 20px; background: #8B0000; border-radius: 15px 15px 0 0;\"></div>\r\n\r\n        <!-- 底部流苏 -->\r\n        <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: -25px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 2px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 25px; background: #8B0000; animation: swayLeft 3s ease-in-out infinite;\"></div>\r\n            <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 20px; background: #8B0000; animation: swayMiddle 3s ease-in-out infinite;\"></div>\r\n            <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 25px; background: #8B0000; animation: swayRight 3s ease-in-out infinite;\"></div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n@keyframes gentleWave {\r\n    0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-1deg); }\r\n    50% { transform: rotate(1deg); }\r\n}\r\n\r\n@keyframes swayLeft {\r\n    0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-5deg); }\r\n    50% { transform: rotate(5deg); }\r\n}\r\n\r\n@keyframes swayMiddle {\r\n    0%, 100% { transform: rotate(3deg); }\r\n    